drawnet.lib.solvers
Class SolverEvent

java.lang.Object
  drawnet.lib.solvers.SolverEvent

public class SolverEvent
extends java.lang.Object

A class representing events in a SolverListener. Available events are:

  • SE_STATUS_CHANGED: the status of the solver has changed (both value and label).
  • SE_STATUS_VALUE_CHANGED: only the status value of the solver has changed.
  • SE_STATUS_LABEL_CHANGED: only the status label of the solver has changed.
  • SE_SOLVER_STOP: the solver stopped.
  • SE_SOLVER_FAIL: the solver failed due to some reason.
  • SE_SOLVER_SUCCESS: the solver succeded.
  • SE_SOLVER_STDOUT: the solver generated some output on standard output.
  • SE_SOLVER_STDERR: the solver generated some output on standard error.
  • SE_SOLVER_ERROR: generic solver error. getEventText() can be invoked for more details on the error.
  • SE_FILE_CHANGED: one of monitored files has changed.
